<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 12:39:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>能量损失在宏观尺度上触发类量子热霍尔效应</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/energy-loss-triggers-quantum-thermal-hall-like-effect-at-macroscopic-scale</link><description>在许多量子材料中——由量子力学效应驱动的具有不寻常电学和磁学特性的材料——电子可以将自己组织成朗道能级，本质上是带电粒子在磁场中运动时形成的量子能态。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/energy-loss-triggers-quantum-thermal-hall-like-effect-at-macroscopic-scale2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 12:39:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/energy-loss-triggers-quantum-thermal-hall-like-effect-at-macroscopic-scale</guid></item><item><title>计算是什么意思？框架映射自然动态系统中运行的隐藏计算</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/what-does-it-mean-to-compute-framework-maps-hidden-computations-running-inside-natural-dynamic-systems</link><description>有些计算机很容易被发现。人造计算机（如智能手机和笔记本电脑中的计算机）是抽象的动态系统，具有可观察的计算元素，如输入、输出、能源成本和逻辑过程。其他计算机则不那么容易被识别。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/what-does-it-mean-to-compute-framework-maps-hidden-computations-running-inside-natural-dynamic-systems.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 12:24:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/what-does-it-mean-to-compute-framework-maps-hidden-computations-running-inside-natural-dynamic-systems</guid></item><item><title>智能材料和药物输送可以利用在干燥界面重组的脂质分子</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/smart-materials-and-drug-delivery-could-exploit-lipid-molecules-that-reorganize-at-drying-interfaces</link><description>湿度水平的微小变化可以促进脂质分子在生物材料或生物膜中重组自身。这会影响皮肤、肺部和泪膜如何保护我们免受脱水。瑞典隆德大学的这一新发现可能会成为智能材料和新药物输送技术的灵感。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/smart-materials-and-drug-delivery-could-exploit-lipid-molecules-that-reorganize-at-drying-interfaces.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 12:09:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/smart-materials-and-drug-delivery-could-exploit-lipid-molecules-that-reorganize-at-drying-interfaces</guid></item><item><title>超薄膜新的、有用的吸收极限</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/a-new-useful-absorption-limit-for-ultra-thin-films</link><description>超薄导电薄膜（例如由以下材料制成的薄膜）的应用&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-new-useful-absorption-limit-for-ultra-thin-films.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 11:54:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/a-new-useful-absorption-limit-for-ultra-thin-films</guid></item><item><title>里德伯原子检测到手持收音机发出的清晰信号</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/rydberg-atoms-detect-clear-signals-from-a-handheld-radio</link><description>美国研究人员团队首次使用含有高激发里德伯原子的传感器来检测来自普通手持无线电的信号。通过仔细地解调输入信号，Noah Schlossberger 和美国国家标准技术研究院 (NIST) 的同事能够恢复多个公共无线电频道中编码的音频，这对消费电子产品的日常使用具有良好的影响。该研究发表于&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/rydberg-atoms-detect-clear-signals-from-a-handheld-radio.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 11:39:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/rydberg-atoms-detect-clear-signals-from-a-handheld-radio</guid></item><item><title>解决行业繁重的泡沫问题</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/tackling-industrys-burdensome-bubble-problem</link><description>在世界各地的工厂中，微小的气泡会造成大问题。气泡会堵塞过滤器、破坏化学反应、降低生物制造过程中的产量，甚至可能导致电子设备和核电站过热。麻省理工学院教授克里帕·瓦拉纳西长期以来一直在研究减少气泡破裂的方法。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/tackling-industrys-burdensome-bubble-problem.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 11:24:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/tackling-industrys-burdensome-bubble-problem</guid></item><item><title>为什么不能在四个维度打结</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/why-you-cant-tie-knots-in-four-dimensions</link><description>我们都知道我们生活在三维空间中。但是当人们谈论四个维度时，这意味着什么呢？它只是一个更大的空间吗？是不是“&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/why-you-cant-tie-knots-in-four-dimensions.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 11:09:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/why-you-cant-tie-knots-in-four-dimensions</guid></item><item><title>跳跃的水坑：气泡破裂揭示了莲花状表面上的水</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/a-puddle-that-jumps-what-bubble-bursts-reveal-about-water-on-lotus-like-surfaces</link><description>水滴具有独特的能力：它们可以自行从表面跳跃。发生这种情况的原因有多种，例如当表面排斥水时或涉及热量时，例如水滴或油滴掠过热锅。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-puddle-that-jumps-what-bubble-bursts-reveal-about-water-on-lotus-like-surfaces.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 10:54:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/a-puddle-that-jumps-what-bubble-bursts-reveal-about-water-on-lotus-like-surfaces</guid></item><item><title>有缺陷的晶体如何为太阳能的未来提供动力</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/how-flawed-crystals-are-powering-the-future-of-solar-energy</link><description>填充缺陷的卤化铅钙钛矿可与硅太阳能电池媲美，因为材料内部的畴壁可分隔并引导电荷。研究人员使用一种新颖的银染色技术将这些电荷传输网络可视化，解决了长期存在的效率之谜。钙钛矿由&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/how-flawed-crystals-are-powering-the-future-of-solar-energy3.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 10:39:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/how-flawed-crystals-are-powering-the-future-of-solar-energy</guid></item><item><title>量子隐形传态突破一次传送 5 个状态</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/quantum-teleportation-breakthrough-sends-5-states-at-once</link><description>中国的一个团队展示了连续变量系统中多个边带量子模式的同时隐形传输，克服了长期存在的技术障碍。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/quantum-teleportation-breakthrough-sends-5-states-at-once.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 10:24:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/02/quantum-teleportation-breakthrough-sends-5-states-at-once</guid></item></channel></rss>